Trial Date Set for Bush, Others: U.S. District Judge Sherman Finesilver 
scheduled an Oct. 7, 1991 trial date for a $200-million civil lawsuit against 
Neil Bush and other key figures in the collapse of Silverado Savings &amp; 
Loan. 
