<TEXT>
<P>
Nine scientists missing for four days in the Piedmontese Alps were found dead 
today, buried under mounds of snow from an avalanche, authorities said. 
</P>
<P>
The bodies were recovered at dawn in a remote valley after a search by 70 
rescuers and three helicopters. 
</P>
